ComicInfo.Title: Murder By Another Name, Part IV: The Autopsy
ComicInfo.Summary:
Expanding the universe of Image's Eisner-nominated series KILLADELPHIA comes a terrifying new tie-in horror series created by acclaimed Marvel writer Rodney Barnes and fan-favorite SPAWN artist Jason Shawn Alexander.
A killer from the annals of history returns for revenge and Nita must uncover why this murderous figure is rampaging through the city. But it's more than just a bloody string of serial killings this time as deadly visions haunt Nitaâ€™s dreams and not even the warnings of her dead brother Jason can save her!
